high_descs: Turn left and veer left to the stove.
Pick up the pan on the left side of the stove.
Turn around and walk to the fridge.
Place the pan on the top shelf of the fridge and close the door. Wait a moment, and take the pan back out.
Turn around and walk back to the stove.
Place the pan on the back right burner.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled pan on a stove.

high_descs: Go to the left around the counter and face the stove.
Pick up the pan from the stove.
Turn to the right and go towards the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator, place the pan inside, close the refrigerator, wait a second, open the refrigerator and remove the pan.
Turn around and head towards the stove.
Place the pan on the burner on the stove.
anns.task_desc: Place the pan on the burner on the stove.

high_descs: walk on over to the kitchen stove
take the sauce pan off of the back left burner
walk with the sauce pan over to the fridge
open the fridge and put the sauce pan in, once it's cooled take it back out
take the sauce pan and walk it over to the kitchen stove
place it on the back right burner this time
anns.task_desc: put the cooled off sauce pan back on the stove
